title: OPL Week 1 Highlights

embed.description: The highlights of the week 1 of the 2016 Oceanic Professional League. www.facebook.com/AbyssEsportsOCE Results Legacy defeated Sin Gaming 2-0 Avant defeated Hellions 2-0 Chiefs defeated Trident 2-0 Dire Wolves defeated Infernum 2-0 http://oce.lolesports.com/

body:
Hey guys, a friend of mine has made an OPL highlights video for the first week in case some of you guys missed out on watching.

If you do end up watching, would love for you to leave some feedback here as these will be produced weekly.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3k1nCNJxQmE
